      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/Toon-in-his-booking-photo.-Screenshot-Fox-12-Ne.jpg?fit=1080%2C610&amp;quality=60&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/Toon-in-his-booking-photo.-Screenshot-Fox-12-Ne.jpg?fit=1080%2C610&amp;quality=60&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/Toon-in-his-booking-photo.-Screenshot-Fox-12-Ne.jpg?fit=1080%2C610&amp;quality=60&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/Toon-in-his-booking-photo.-Screenshot-Fox-12-Ne.jpg?fit=1080%2C610&amp;quality=60&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/Toon-in-his-booking-photo.-Screenshot-Fox-12-Ne.jpg?fit=1080%2C610&amp;quality=60&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/Toon-in-his-booking-photo.-Screenshot-Fox-12-Ne.jpg?fit=1080%2C610&amp;quality=60&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/Toon-in-his-booking-photo.-Screenshot-Fox-12-Ne.jpg?fit=1080%2C610&amp;quality=60&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/Toon-in-his-booking-photo.-Screenshot-Fox-12-Ne.jpg?fit=1080%2C610&amp;quality=60&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<a href=\"https://boingboing.net/2026/05/31/loony-toon-sentenced.html\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Loony Toon sentenced to 20 years in prison for shooting at cops\"><img alt=\"Toon in his booking photo. Screenshot: Fox 12 News\" class=\"webfeedsFeaturedVisual wp-post-image\" height=\"610\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/Toon-in-his-booking-photo.-Screenshot-Fox-12-Ne.jpg?fit=1080%2C610&amp;quality=60&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"display: block; margin: auto; margin-bottom: 5px;\" width=\"1080\" /></a><p>A man was sentenced to 20 years imprisonment after admitting he took shots at police in Milwaukie, Oregon, while fleeing a traffic stop. <a href=\"https://www.wtoc.com/2026/05/30/man-named-loony-toon-sentenced-shooting-3-officers/\">Loony Tune, 43, pleaded guilty to four counts of first-degree attempted assault</a> and other crimes. Already a convited felon, the sentence was a plea deal arranged with Clackamas County District Attorney's Office. &#8212; <a class=\"read-more\" href=\"https://boingboing.net/2026/05/31/loony-toon-sentenced.html\">Read the rest </a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://boingboing.net/2026/05/31/loony-toon-sentenced.html\">Loony Toon sentenced to 20 years in prison for shooting at cops</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://boingboing.net\">Boing Boing</a>.</p>",
